title: philteds Dash Stroller in Red
text: Phil&Teds Dash Stroller in red Stroller Originally Posted On: Feed Services Additional Comments: The modern and stylish Dash Stroller is beautifully tailored for urban adventures in cities and parks. With stylish marbled fabric options, dash is dressed to impress. It is easy to pop up over curbs in the city and very light with a compact one piece stand fold. The option for a 2nd seat attached to the underside allows you to carry 1 or two kids.The wheels offer the smoothest ride, puncture free, so they can ride over any terrain and no flat tires. It is travel system compatible as well! Features: hand operated parking brake for ease of use integrated back screen to protect from the elements flip out support for little legs front suspension with 10" aerotech wheel secure storage pocket with headphone jack safe and easy 5-point harness with 1 touch release curb hop light and easy compact fold 2nd seat optional 45 x 25 x 45/51.5"
